<h3 id="installation">Installation</h3>

<p>Step 1. Download the file <a href="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/jhvanderschee/jekyllcodex/gh-pages/_includes/accordion.html">accordion.html</a>
<br />Step 2. Save the file in the ‘_includes’ directory of your project
<br />Step 3. Make sure the bottom of your layout document looks like this:</p>

<pre><code>...
{% include accordion.html %}

</code></pre>
